<figureCitation box="[271,314,1362,1386]" captionStart="FIGURES 135–141" captionStartId="73.[151,264,1934,1957]" captionTargetBox="[233,1354,167,1912]" captionTargetId="figure-81@73.[233,1354,167,1912]" captionTargetPageId="73" captionText="FIGURES 135–141. Diagrams with distribution records for: 135, Debilos curtuvenatum sp. nov.; 136, D. labeculatum sp. nov.; 137, D. melachrosatum sp. nov.; 138, D. nivatum sp. nov.; 139, D. petiolatum sp. nov.; 140, D. trochanteratum (Szépligeti); 141, D. xanthochrosatum sp. nov." pageId="26" pageNumber="27">137</figureCitation>
